abstract: Carl C. Icahn disclosed on Wednesday that he had raised his stake in the online health company yet again, to 13.12 percent from 11.64 percent.
snippet: Carl C. Icahn disclosed on Wednesday that he had raised his stake in the online health company yet again, to 13.12 percent from 11.64 percent.
lead_paragraph: Carl C. Icahn appears far from done with WebMD.

headline.main: Icahn Raises Stake in WebMD Again

byline.original: By Michael J. de la Merced
